@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

state "Waiting for Sale" as WS
state "NewItemEntry" as NIE
state "Payment" as P
state "Sale Completed" as SC

WS : entry / System starts waiting for a new sale
WS : do / Waits for new sale initiation

NIE : entry / System starts accepting items
NIE : do / Enters items one by one
NIE : exit / All items have been added

P : entry / System moves to payment after items are added
P : do / Processes payment method

SC : entry / Sale is completed
SC : exit / Returns to waiting for next sale

WS --> NIE : New sale starts
NIE --> P : All items added
P --> SC : Cash payment
P --> P : Card or Check payment
SC --> WS : Return to waiting

@enduml
